typeProperties.script:
source(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	httpMethod: 'GET',
	timeout: 30,
	responseFormat: ['type' -> 'json', 'documentForm' -> 'arrayOfDocuments']) ~> restbby
restbby derive() ~> DerivedColumn1
DerivedColumn1 sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: true,
	input(
		country as string,
		Partner as string,
		Year as short,
		month as short,
		month_presence as double,
		country_name as string
	),
	format: 'parquet',
	partitionFileNames:['census_parquet'],
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true,
	saveOrder: 1,
	partitionBy('hash', 1)) ~> sink1
